<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>🔓 Knock</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Convert ACSM files to DRM-free EPUB files</p>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="intro">
            <p>This web interface provides a user-friendly way to use Knock, a tool that converts ACSM files to DRM-free EPUB files.</p>
            <p><strong>Note:</strong> This web application runs actual Knock CLI tools on the server. Check the System Status section below to see if all dependencies are available.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="converter-section">
            <h2>Convert Your ACSM File</h2>
            
            <form id="conversion-form" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                <div class="step-container">
                    <div class="step">
                        <h3>Step 1: Adobe Account</h3>
                        <p>You need a free Adobe account. <a href="https://account.adobe.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Create one here</a> if you don't have one.</p>
                        
                        <div class="input-group">
                            <label for="adobe-email">Adobe Email:</label>
                            <input type="email" id="adobe-email" name="adobeEmail" placeholder="your@email.com" required />
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="input-group">
                            <label for="adobe-password">Adobe Password:</label>
                            <input type="password" id="adobe-password" name="adobePassword" placeholder="Your password" required />
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="step">
                        <h3>Step 2: Upload ACSM File</h3>
                        <p>Select your ACSM file to convert:</p>
                        
                        <div class="file-upload">
                            <input type="file" id="acsm-file" name="acsmFile" accept=".acsm" required />
                            <label for="acsm-file" class="file-label">
                                <span class="file-text">Choose ACSM file</span>
                            </label>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="file-info" id="file-info"></div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="step">
                        <h3>Step 3: Process File</h3>
                        <button type="submit" id="process-btn" class="process-btn">
                            Start Conversion
                        </button>
                        
                        <div class="progress-area" id="progress-area" style="display: none;">
                            <div class="progress-bar">
                                <div class="progress-fill" id="progress-fill"></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="status-text" id="status-text">Processing...</div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="result-area" id="result-area" style="display: none;">
                            <h4>Conversion Complete!</h4>
                            <p id="result-message">Your DRM-free EPUB file is ready for download.</p>
                            <a href="#" class="download-btn" id="download-btn">Download EPUB</a>
                        </div>

                        <div class="error-area" id="error-area" style="display: none;">
                            <h4>Error</h4>
                            <p id="error-message"></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </form>
        </section>

        <section class="status-section">
            <h2>System Status</h2>
            <div id="system-status">
                <p>Loading system status...</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="installation-section">
            <h2>CLI Installation (Alternative)</h2>
            <p>For direct CLI usage, install Knock on your system:</p>
            
            <div class="installation-tabs">
                <button class="tab-btn active" data-tab="nixos">NixOS</button>
                <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="linux">Linux</button>
            </div>
            
            <div class="tab-content active" data-tab="nixos">
                <pre><code># Add to your system flake.nix
inputs.knock.url = github:BentonEdmondson/knock
outputs = { self, knock }: { /* knock.defaultPackage.x86_64-linux is the package */ }

# Then run:
knock ~/path/to/my-book.acsm</code></pre>
            </div>
            
            <div class="tab-content" data-tab="linux">
                <pre><code># Download the latest release
# Make it executable
chmod +x knock-version-x86_64-linux
mv knock-version-x86_64-linux knock

# Run conversion
./knock ~/path/to/my-book.acsm</code></pre>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="sources-section">
            <h2>Verified Book Sources</h2>
            <p>Knock has been verified to work with ACSM files from:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="https://www.ebooks.com/en-us/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">eBooks.com</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://www.kobo.com/us/en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Rakuten Kobo</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://books.google.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Books</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://www.hugendubel.de/de/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hugendubel.de</a> (German)</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
            <h2>Legal Notice</h2>
            <div class="legal-content">
                <p><strong>Important:</strong> <a href="https://gizmodo.com/its-perfectly-legal-to-tell-people-how-to-remove-drm-1670223538" target="_blank" rel="noopener">It's Perfectly Legal to Tell People How to Remove DRM</a> (Gizmodo)</p>
                
                <p><strong>Do not use this software for piracy; this software is not intended for piracy.</strong> This software exists to allow readers to <em>legally</em> purchase and then legally and <em>freely</em> read ebooks.</p>
                
                <p>This software exists to <em>incentivize</em> the legal purchase of ebooks by enabling their unrestricted and legal consumption.</p>
                
                <p class="license-info">This software is licensed under GPLv3. The resulting EPUB files can be read with any EPUB reader.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>Knock - Licensed under GPLv3 | <a href="https://github.com/BentonEdmondson/knock" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub Repository</a></p>
    </footer>

    <script src="/js/app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>